{"tid":133414,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"失業/Part-time/Freelance 幫巴打免費搵工Telegram Whatsapp Group！","createTime":"2017-02-24T14:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T03:10:46.000Z","uid":38706,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"226f5218b51a7c7c59495cd23f38d50755e82559","tid":133414,"uid":38706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:49:09.000Z","msg":"廢話喺下面！一句講曬，想免費搵工就telegram我！(下面有未來計劃同點解搞個Group)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ashfbnjxje\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fashfbnjxje&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=718cc518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ashfbnjxje</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說小弟做咗廿年人無咩成功但叫有個目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係想做到個完整嘅Part-Time/Freelance平台比到香港人用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而其實喺過去半年我都叫幫到幾個巴打搵到唔同工種(freelance/part-time/full-time) 所以想將依樣嘢進一步幫到更多巴打！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMini Q&amp;A<br />\n會有咩工呢？<br />\n會有唔同freelance(寫嘢/web/執圖) / part-time (sales/侍應/data-entry/etc) / 甚至full time!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想點搞？<br />\n會先form個telegram group 知道有幾多個巴打想搵工，然後再根據噤多位巴絲所長幫你做job-pairing! Whatsapp Group開唔開得成就睇有幾多巴打join~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係唔洗錢？<br />\n係！只係見得閒無嘢做又有好幾份job想請人所以想服務吓連巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783a628e2e174f78ce2f999682f01efdeacc4bdd","tid":133414,"uid":38706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:16:40.000Z","msg":"有幾個巴打tg好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但夜已深 巴打今晚tg 就會聽朝入到group<br />\n最快聽日開始會有工post出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n輕輕一推～"},{"pid":"8c430a009cdabea07ddb9a2e27f845ab8aff8975","tid":133414,"uid":41388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:34:39.000Z","msg":"支持下巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35489e768f4d6aaafe546a568edcaaadba43d1ee","tid":133414,"uid":87298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1457fd754e905b809a8b65f344719feccdf132db","tid":133414,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:27:35.000Z","msg":"巴打，我加左了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d81f83443a5c6d26587e090b169df87bcb1743","tid":133414,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"d70a77c2a2435017fc9f6d4bd2de4aa5b715be14","tid":133414,"uid":8103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:47:27.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7aedd07c09c448ffbec2eec688d5e4f1396937","tid":133414,"uid":74110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:16:07.000Z","msg":"而家好似有個apps叫炒散王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be91991e7a36514babdf9b99a61428c6f8fe9e61","tid":133414,"uid":74110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家好似