":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:11:22.000Z","msg":"見好多巴絲有疑問 究竟我係唔係蛇頭呢？<br />\n答案係：唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時我做到嘅會係你唔用佢都搵到啲好工返嚟(可能係jobsdb indeed)，就幫大家screen啲比較好嘅工出嚟<br />\n然後就放係group度等大家自己申請去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過程中我唔會行巴打同埋間公司入邊收到任何錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而可能遲啲會同其他job agency合佢，做direct job mayching，upgrade我依家做緊嘅嘢，不過就後話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最終係想做到一個完善freelance part time平台！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ce63c37f52a17d17fd9a986e8a97f0eb7711aa","tid":133414,"uid":38706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家好似有個apps叫炒散王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbtw 加油</blockquote><br />\n多謝，我要都會有炒散工嘅<br />\n但唔會多囉<br />\n<br />\n始終炒散嘅工大家巴打容易搵到啦，係想搵啲可能真係筍啲嘅工，又少有嘅俾大家去做個參考"},{"pid":"b4f5bef8a1980d53bb96b860f8c7c0a6381c9d07","tid":133414,"uid":1495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:23:39.000Z","msg":"幫樓主推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6509acf35c3e19494e7c1dda382236cb0f024105","tid":133414,"uid":73257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:45:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d5d8c7451d9e78c035f71bc72a38c35e6e8f60","tid":133414,"uid":38706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T03:00:25.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"b205c95339328c327b3128d0c251